@startuml
title Decorator

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Attach responsibilities to objects dynamically; flexible alternative to subclassing.

**Use when**: Need to add features to instances at runtime.

**Key participants**: Component, ConcreteComponent, Decorator, ConcreteDecorator.
endlegend

interface Component {
  +operation()
}

abstract class Decorator implements Component {
  -component : Component
  +operation()
}

class ConcreteComponent
class ConcreteDecoratorA
class ConcreteDecoratorB

Component <|.. ConcreteComponent
Decorator <|-- ConcreteDecoratorA
Decorator <|-- ConcreteDecoratorB
Decorator o-- Component
@enduml